### File Operations API Tests
### Tests for FileOperationsController endpoints
### Base URL: http://localhost:8080
### OpenCode server: http://localhost:4096

### Get file tree
### Returns hierarchical tree structure of project files
GET http://localhost:8080/api/files/tree
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get file tree with path filter
### Returns file tree starting from specified path
GET http://localhost:8080/api/files/tree?path=src/main/java
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get file content
### Returns content of a specific file
GET http://localhost:8080/api/files/content?path=src/main/java/opencode/Main.java
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Search in files
### Search for text pattern in project files
GET http://localhost:8080/api/files/search?pattern=OpenCode&path=src
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Find files by name pattern
### Find files matching a name pattern
GET http://localhost:8080/api/files/find?pattern=*.java
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get file symbols
### Returns code symbols (classes, methods, etc.) from a file
GET http://localhost:8080/api/files/symbols?path=src/main/java/opencode/Main.java
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get file diff
### Returns git diff for a file
GET http://localhost:8080/api/files/diff?path=src/main/java/opencode/Main.java
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get file status
### Returns git status for files in the project
GET http://localhost:8080/api/files/status
Content-Type: application/json

###
